## Milestone details

In the [v0.16.0](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues?q=milestone:v0.16.0) scope, 
16 issues were resolved and 31 pull requests were merged.
This release includes 39 commits by 7 contributors.

## Resolved issues (16)

* [#1133](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/1133) BenchmarkDotNet (arguably) slightly overcorrects for overhead (assignee: [@timcassell](https://github.com/timcassell))
* [#1197](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/1197) Enable including references in autogenerated csproject (assignee: [@timcassell](https://github.com/timcassell))
* [#1499](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/1499) Cross platform disassembler doensn't output anything on macOS (assignee: [@timcassell](https://github.com/timcassell))
* [#2305](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2305) overhead and workload invocation sequences diverge (assignee: [@timcassell](https://github.com/timcassell))
* [#2344](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2344) Build fails when returning type from PackageReference (assignee: [@timcassell](https://github.com/timcassell))
* [#2371](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2371) Generated benchmarks ignore --framework flag when running out of process (assignee: [@timcassell](https://github.com/timcassell))
* [#2530](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2530) Support for F# anonymous records
* [#2669](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2669) Only Windows and Linux are supported in DisassemblyDiagnoser
* [#2789](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2789) `test-windows-full` CI job failed on disassemble tests for x86 (assignee: [@timcassell](https://github.com/timcassell))
* [#2821](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2821) Build error when using certain method names (assignee: [@User0332](https://github.com/User0332))
* [#2838](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2838) Ratio does not get reset for new input set when using ArgumentsSource (assignee: [@User0332](https://github.com/User0332))
* [#2861](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2861) Move RunningEmptyBenchmarkTests from unit tests to integration tests
* [#2891](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2891) Multi-dimensional arrays are displayed as single-dimensional (assignee: [@User0332](https://github.com/User0332))
* [#2893](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2893) Mixed multidimensional & jagged arrays cause compilation errors (assignee: [@User0332](https://github.com/User0332))
* [#2896](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2896) DotNetSdkValidator failed when using CsProjClassicNetToolchain (assignee: [@filzrev](https://github.com/filzrev))
* [#2917](https://github.com/dotnet/BenchmarkDotNet/issues/2917) Test Report failure (assignee: [@timcassell](https://github.com/timcassell))
